        "meta_description": "Kameron Hurley’s new military science fiction novel depicts a soldier’s fight in a brutal corporate war. Teleported to the battlefield in a beam of light, Dietz gets unstuck in time, and has to find a way to control her life and the war. It’s a worthy successor to classic novels like Starship Troopers and The Forever War.",
        "meta_lang": "en",
